---
// Cluster composition demo
---

<div class="flow flow-space-md">
    <h2>Cluster Composition</h2>
    <p>
        The cluster composition groups elements together with consistent
        spacing. It's perfect for navigation, buttons, or any grouped elements.
    </p>

    <div class="cluster cluster-gap-sm">
        <h3>Small Gap Cluster</h3>
        <button class="btn">Button 1</button>
        <button class="btn">Button 2</button>
        <button class="btn">Button 3</button>
    </div>

    <div class="cluster cluster-gap-md">
        <h3>Medium Gap Cluster</h3>
        <span class="badge">Tag 1</span>
        <span class="badge">Tag 2</span>
        <span class="badge">Tag 3</span>
        <span class="badge">Tag 4</span>
    </div>

    <div class="cluster cluster-gap-lg cluster-justify-center">
        <h3>Centered Large Gap Cluster</h3>
        <a href="#" class="link">Link 1</a>
        <a href="#" class="link">Link 2</a>
        <a href="#" class="link">Link 3</a>
    </div>

    <div class="cluster cluster-gap-xl cluster-justify-end">
        <h3>Right-Aligned Cluster</h3>
        <button class="btn btn-secondary">Cancel</button>
        <button class="btn btn-primary">Save</button>
    </div>
</div>
